{"type":"message","id":"87277e9f","parentId":"8313a134","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:45:37.882Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个地址看起来像是一个本地或内网的 OpenClaw WebChat 地址（`https://172.16.117.156/chat`），但它不是公开的 WebChat 服务。以下是关键点：\n\n1. **IP 地址**：`172.16.117.156` 是一个内网 IP 地址（属于私有地址范围 `172.16.0.0/12`），通常用于局域网或企业内部网络。\n2. **路径**：`/chat` 是 OpenClaw WebChat 的默认路径。\n3. **参数**：`session=agent%3Amain%3Amain` 表示这是一个 OpenClaw 代理会话的链接。\n\n### 结论\n这是一个 **内网部署的 OpenClaw WebChat 地址**，不是公开的 WebChat 服务。如果你能访问该内网，可以通过这个地址使用 WebChat。\n\n需要进一步帮助吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"DeepSeek-V3-0324","usage":{"input":19850,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20043,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773546333622}}
{"type":"message","id":"067e9d5c","parentId":"87277e9f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:46:17.381Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sun 2026-03-15 11:46 GMT+8] webchat是 channel的一种吗"}],"timestamp":1773546377380}}
{"type":"message","id":"3722a985","parentId":"067e9d5c","timestamp":"2026-03-15T03:46:20.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"是的，**WebChat** 是 OpenClaw 支持的通信渠道（channel）之一。在 OpenClaw 中，`channel` 指的是消息传递的媒介或平台，比如：\n\n- **WebChat**（网页聊天界面）\n- **Telegram**（Telegram 机器人）\n- **Discord**（Discord 机器人）\n- **WhatsApp**（通过 WhatsApp Business API）\n- **Signal**（通过 Signal 桥接）\n- **Feishu**（飞书）\n- **其他支持的平台**\n\n### WebChat 的特点\n1. **直接访问**：通过浏览器打开，无需额外安装应用。\n2. **内网/公网部署**：可以运行在本地（如 `http://localhost`）或服务器（如 `https://your-domain.com`）。\n3. **轻量级**：适合快速调试或临时会话。\n\n### 与其他 Channel 的区别\n- **WebChat** 是 OpenClaw 自带的默认 Web 界面，而其他渠道（如 Telegram、Discord）需要额外配置 API 或机器人令牌。\n- WebChat 通常用于开发、测试或内部管理，而其他渠道可能用于正式的用户交互。\n\n如果需要切换或配置其他 channel，可以通过 OpenClaw 的配置文件或命令行工具设置。需要进一步帮助吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"DeepSeek-V3-0324","usage":{"input":20102,"output":276,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20378,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773546377381}}
