{"type":"message","id":"f8647076","parentId":"85a6e558","timestamp":"2026-03-15T04:00:49.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"要使用 **方法1** 通过命令行确认定时任务是否添加成功，可以运行以下命令：\n\nbash\nopenclaw cron list\n\n\n这条命令会列出当前所有已配置的定时任务（包括名称、时间规则和提醒内容）。  \n\n---\n\n### 预期输出示例：\njson\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"午饭提醒\",\n    \"schedule\": {\n      \"kind\": \"cron\",\n      \"expr\": \"0 12 * * *\",\n      \"tz\": \"Asia/Hong_Kong\"\n    },\n    \"payload\": {\n      \"kind\": \"systemEvent\",\n      \"text\": \"记得按时吃饭啦！🍚\"\n    }\n  }\n]\n\n\n如果输出为空数组 `[]`，则说明任务未添加成功。  \n\n---\n\n### 如果需要，我可以直接通过工具调用帮你查询（无需手动输入命令）：\njson\n{\n  \"action\": \"list\"\n}\n\n\n请告诉我你更倾向于哪种方式！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"DeepSeek-V3-0324","usage":{"input":22485,"output":204,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773547247297}}
